\F[beni_true]Akane: "We, the Banter Agents, are 'Modified Humans' who
have obtained power far beyond humans through the power of
spiritual liquor, but we have a weakness of being easily
swept away by pleasure."

hands with Nadeshiko!"

enemies."

everyone die."

\F[beni_trouble]Akane: "That's why I'm truly grateful for the cooperation of
Nadeshiko and the others. However... it will definitely
expose them to danger. I really need to figure out
something..."

\F[beni_angry2]Akane: (First, it might be good to hear the details from
